<h2>About us</h2>

<p align="justify">We are from fertile PR ground. We can help with all aspects of reputation management and reputation drives media relations and word of mouth marketing, which are the most effective forms of marketing.</p>

<p align="justify">PR House Co., Ltd. is an independent public relations firm in Korea. We are an affiliated company of HPR &amp; Company founded in 1986, Korea&rsquo;s first PR agency, which has been fertile ground for PR House. We were born from the company in 2010 to focus more on providing clients with the best in creative integrated communications, effective and measurable implementation, and communications counsel. We provide clients with the best solutions and the most effective way to change the rules in the client&rsquo;s favor.</p>

<p align="justify">We utilize our broad range of integrated services across multiple industries &ndash; consumer marketing, corporate communications, digital media strategies, public affairs, government relations, technology and healthcare. With in-depth communications expertise, we help clients inform the people they need to reach. We have built our reputation by delivering demonstrable value to our clients from multinational corporations to governmental bodies; from industry leaders to entrepreneurs. With our global partnership, we have the ability to deliver our clients&rsquo; messages both at home and abroad.</p>

<p align="justify">Our diverse and hands-on expertise comes from the environments clients need to reach &ndash; we have all been leaders in different areas: business executives in multinational companies in Europe and Asian countries, journalists, global marketing leaders, digital experts, and others. That helps us provide and implement strategic and tailored services to meet clients&rsquo; needs.</p>

<p align="justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p align="justify"><strong>HPR &amp; Company</strong></p>

<p align="justify">Today, good communications are recognized as the lifeblood of any organization. Because of this, organizations are sending one type of message or another to their target audience in the manner that may be most naturally and effectively accepted by their target audience. HPR is an independent and indigenous PR and communication consultancy in Korea since 1986. Further information on HPR &amp; Company can be found at www.hprco.com</p>

